text: D'Acquisto is the surname of: * John D'Acquisto (born 1951), American former Major League Baseball pitcher * Mario D'Acquisto, president of Sicily from 1980 to 1982 - see List of presidents of Sicily * Salvo D'Acquisto (1920–1943), member of the Italian Carabinieri who sacrificed himself to save 22 civilians from execution
title: D'Acquisto
